Class Element21

  element.Element
      element.Element2D

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Element21
extends Element2D

Class for Element21. Properties of element are; Mechanics: Sanders' doubly-curved shell, Geometric: Linear, Material: Orthotropic/Isotropic, Interpolation degree: Biquadratic, Interpolation family: Lagrange, Number of nodes: 6, Geometry: Triangular, Dofs (per node): ux, uy, uz, rx, ry, rz (global), u1, u2, u3, r1, r2 (local), Mechanical loading: fx, fy, fz, mx, my, mz (global), f1, f2, f3, m1, m2 (local), Temperature loading: yes, Displacements: u1, u2, u3, r1, r2, Strains: e11, e22, e12, e13, e23 Stresses: s11, s22, s33, s12, s13, s23, Internal forces: P11, N22, Q12, F13, H23, K22, M11, T12. Radii of curvatures, r1 and r2 in both directions are given as parameters. Note: Transverse shear and bending-membrane coupling terms are under-integrated against shear and membrane locking.

Author:
Murat
